Ingredients:			               				   

2 celery bunches

1 bunch of spinach

1 bunch of kale

<3 makes enough green juice for 2 <3 

Method:

1. Add ingredients to a high quality juicer.

1. Strain juice if necessary before adding to your favorite juice jars/glasses.
